WEBVTT

00:00:09.208 --> 00:00:10.375
Speak up.

00:00:10.417 --> 00:00:13.417
I want to know
what your ultimate dream is.

00:00:13.458 --> 00:00:16.333
That is a student's
primary duty here, after all.

00:00:16.375 --> 00:00:17.875
For the moment,
why don't you make it

00:00:17.917 --> 00:00:20.250
your objective to become a Bet?

00:00:21.708 --> 00:00:24.833
I shall wait for you
to stand by me. Sound good?

00:00:26.875 --> 00:00:28.917
[NARRATOR]
Iruma Suzuki, age 14.

00:00:28.958 --> 00:00:30.125
One day, he found himself

00:00:30.167 --> 00:00:32.167
the grandson
of a demon named Sullivan.

00:00:33.208 --> 00:00:35.458
Sullivan loves and spoils Iruma

00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:36.667
and is even sending him

00:00:36.708 --> 00:00:39.000
to the most prestigious school
in the land.

00:00:39.042 --> 00:00:41.583
But there's just one problem.

00:00:41.625 --> 00:00:44.917
The school Iruma is attending
just so happens to be

00:00:44.958 --> 00:00:47.958
the demon school
known as Babyls.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:50.292
[IRUMA] I can't ever
let them find out I'm human

00:00:50.333 --> 00:00:52.333
or I'm gonna get eaten for sure.

00:02:25.625 --> 00:02:26.833
[IRUMA, ASMODEUS AND CLARA]
"Iruma's Decision

00:02:26.875 --> 00:02:28.208
and Hard Work."

00:02:31.792 --> 00:02:32.792
What?

00:02:32.833 --> 00:02:35.333
So, you want to climb the ranks?

00:02:35.375 --> 00:02:37.833
[IRUMA]
Yeah. Exactly.

00:02:40.583 --> 00:02:43.875
For now, all I wanna do
is climb from Alef to Bet.

00:02:44.875 --> 00:02:46.542
If you don't mind,

00:02:46.583 --> 00:02:49.208
I was hoping you'd be willing
to show me how to do that.

00:02:49.250 --> 00:02:51.292
[gasps] Wha...

00:02:51.333 --> 00:02:52.208
Azz?

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:56.250
[ASMODEUS] I almost thought
Master Iruma had no interest

00:02:56.292 --> 00:02:57.792
in rising in the ranks,

00:02:57.833 --> 00:03:01.208
but I knew it must've been
secretly eating away at him.

00:03:01.250 --> 00:03:02.750
[gulps] What's wrong?

00:03:02.792 --> 00:03:05.167
[ASMODEUS]
And why wouldn't it be?

00:03:05.208 --> 00:03:08.042
Master Iruma did something
as unprecedented as making

00:03:08.083 --> 00:03:10.375
the Guardian of Cutthroat Valley
his pet,

00:03:10.417 --> 00:03:13.042
yet his rank was immeasurable.

00:03:13.083 --> 00:03:15.083
He obviously can't be ranked
on the same scale

00:03:15.125 --> 00:03:16.708
as the rest of us demons,

00:03:16.750 --> 00:03:18.083
but that's no reason
to place him

00:03:18.125 --> 00:03:19.500
at the lowest rank of Alef.

00:03:22.667 --> 00:03:24.542
Believe me,
when you were ranked an Alef,

00:03:24.583 --> 00:03:27.167
I was just as displeased
and confused, as well.

00:03:27.208 --> 00:03:28.625
I was becoming numb

00:03:28.667 --> 00:03:30.417
from all of our
degenerate classmates

00:03:30.458 --> 00:03:31.458
who lack ambition,

00:03:31.500 --> 00:03:32.542
but moving up the ranks

00:03:32.583 --> 00:03:34.333
is a demon's pure pride.

00:03:34.375 --> 00:03:36.292
Let's get you to the top.

00:03:36.333 --> 00:03:37.958
Now, it's time to prepare.

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:39.958
Uh, yeah, sure.

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:41.167
Prepare for what?

00:03:41.208 --> 00:03:42.458
-[ASMODEUS] What else?!
-[BOTH gasp]

00:03:42.500 --> 00:03:44.458
For Master Iruma to quickly soar

00:03:44.500 --> 00:03:46.083
to the highest rank of Yodh,

00:03:46.125 --> 00:03:51.333
and then reign over
the entirety of Babyls!

00:03:52.875 --> 00:03:55.333
[BOTH]
Wha...

00:03:55.375 --> 00:03:57.875
-[BOY 1] What the what?
-[BOY 2] That's crazy ambitious!

00:03:57.917 --> 00:04:00.083
[BOY 3] Another legend's
about to be born!

00:04:01.833 --> 00:04:04.833
I have no doubt Iruma can do it.

00:04:04.875 --> 00:04:06.958
Promotion, please.

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:08.333
[COME-COME]
No, go away.

00:04:08.375 --> 00:04:10.667
Um, hey, Azz,

00:04:10.708 --> 00:04:12.917
I'm totally fine
with just getting to Bet rank.

00:04:12.958 --> 00:04:15.833
Huh? What? But I thought...

00:04:15.875 --> 00:04:17.125
[gasps]

00:04:17.167 --> 00:04:20.500
Nay, this is Master Iruma
we're talking about.

00:04:20.542 --> 00:04:22.250
I'm sure he has
some profound reason

00:04:22.292 --> 00:04:25.083
my feeble little mind
could never even fathom.

00:04:25.125 --> 00:04:27.833
I apologize for
my deplorable presumptuousness.

00:04:27.875 --> 00:04:31.125
Uh, don't worry about it.
I just don't want to stand out!

00:04:31.167 --> 00:04:34.625
Now, Master Iruma
will prepare to rise up

00:04:34.667 --> 00:04:37.125
to the perfectly
respectable rank of Bet.

00:04:37.167 --> 00:04:39.458
Make way!

00:04:39.500 --> 00:04:40.750
[BOY 1]
Really, just Bet?

00:04:40.792 --> 00:04:42.500
[BOY 2]
Well, that's not very ambitious.

00:04:42.542 --> 00:04:44.458
[BOY 3] Who cares?
This is gonna be crazy.

00:04:44.500 --> 00:04:46.125
[BOY 4]
I'm devi psyched for it.

00:04:46.167 --> 00:04:48.375
Oh. what should I do?

00:04:48.417 --> 00:04:49.917
If Iruma goes up to Bet,

00:04:49.958 --> 00:04:52.250
then the two of us
won't be the same rank anymore.

00:04:52.292 --> 00:04:55.125
Well, you could try
to moving up, too, you know.

00:04:57.167 --> 00:04:58.625
[grunts]

00:04:58.667 --> 00:05:00.875
[LEAD]
Hmm.

00:05:00.917 --> 00:05:02.875
That sounds like fun.

00:05:02.917 --> 00:05:05.250
Now, let us go quickly,
Iruma sir.

00:05:05.292 --> 00:05:07.625
-[IRUMA] Uh, sure.
-[CLARA] Wait, wait.

00:05:07.667 --> 00:05:09.250
-[ASMODEUS] Hmm?
-[IRUMA] Huh?

00:05:09.292 --> 00:05:10.875
[COME-COME]
Take her.

00:05:10.917 --> 00:05:12.375
[CLARA]
Yeah, take me away.

00:05:12.417 --> 00:05:14.458
Come on, do it. Do it!

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:22.042
[IRUMA]
Hey, uh, where are we?

00:05:24.250 --> 00:05:26.667
[ASMODEUS] This is
Babyls' underground gym.

00:05:28.208 --> 00:05:31.625
Oh, wow. I never knew
an insane place like this

00:05:31.667 --> 00:05:33.958
was sitting
under our classrooms.

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:35.792
I'm blown away.

00:05:35.833 --> 00:05:37.333
It's huge!

00:05:37.375 --> 00:05:39.208
Hey Connor. Hey, Murf.

00:05:39.250 --> 00:05:41.583
You can run around
all you want down here.

00:05:41.625 --> 00:05:46.583
-And I'm rolling-g-g-g!
-[IRUMA gasps]

00:05:46.625 --> 00:05:48.375
But they're not
doing the running.

00:05:48.417 --> 00:05:50.000
She vexes me so.

00:05:51.750 --> 00:05:52.958
Now, then.

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:54.792
There is currently but one way

00:05:54.833 --> 00:05:56.625
for you to go up a rank, sir.

00:05:56.667 --> 00:05:58.083
And that is to get good marks

00:05:58.125 --> 00:06:00.833
on the periodic promotion exams
we have in class.

00:06:00.875 --> 00:06:02.750
So we've got our work
cut out for us.

00:06:02.792 --> 00:06:04.208
Promotion?

00:06:04.250 --> 00:06:06.000
Exams?

00:06:06.042 --> 00:06:09.333
That's right, and the next one
is only a week away.

00:06:09.375 --> 00:06:11.542
And the ability
we'll be tested on is...

00:06:12.542 --> 00:06:15.250
execution cannonball.

00:06:17.542 --> 00:06:20.250
-Execution?
-Cannibals?

00:06:20.292 --> 00:06:21.458
Cannonball!

00:06:21.500 --> 00:06:24.292
Can't you even
at least pretend to try?

00:06:24.333 --> 00:06:26.833
Execution cannonball
was once used as a test

00:06:26.875 --> 00:06:28.792
to repress a sudden outbreak
of demons

00:06:28.833 --> 00:06:30.792
battling over
their territories.

00:06:30.833 --> 00:06:33.792
It was nothing short
of a total massacre.

00:06:33.833 --> 00:06:36.375
We used weapons called caimans.

00:06:36.417 --> 00:06:38.208
When they bit down
on their prey,

00:06:38.250 --> 00:06:41.208
they wouldn't let go until
only bloody shreds were left.

00:06:41.250 --> 00:06:44.042
[growling]

00:06:47.250 --> 00:06:49.417
The first of them to enter
their enemy's castle

00:06:49.458 --> 00:06:52.708
and eliminate everyone inside
would emerge victorious.

00:06:54.708 --> 00:06:56.958
[gasps] That's horrifying.

00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:59.875
Indeed. But due to
the high casualties...

00:06:59.917 --> 00:07:01.000
[IRUMA gasps]

00:07:01.042 --> 00:07:02.333
...we simply use this ball now

00:07:02.375 --> 00:07:03.208
in lieu of caimans.

00:07:03.250 --> 00:07:04.250
It's safer.

00:07:04.292 --> 00:07:06.250
-That's doable.
-[chuckles]

00:07:06.292 --> 00:07:08.042
[ASMODEUS]
And to conserve time and money,

00:07:08.083 --> 00:07:10.167
we now use these territories
marked by lines

00:07:10.208 --> 00:07:12.042
instead of castles.

00:07:12.083 --> 00:07:13.125
Super effective.

00:07:13.167 --> 00:07:14.500
Those who are hit

00:07:14.542 --> 00:07:16.000
must move to the sidelines.

00:07:16.042 --> 00:07:16.875
[IRUMA]
Makes sense.

00:07:16.917 --> 00:07:19.417
Let's get this thing started.

00:07:19.458 --> 00:07:21.708
But even from the sidelines
you can come back in

00:07:21.750 --> 00:07:24.042
as soon as you hit
an enemy with the ball.

00:07:24.083 --> 00:07:26.250
Valac, you conjure up
the cursed puppets

00:07:26.292 --> 00:07:27.542
so we can have enough players.

00:07:27.583 --> 00:07:29.167
You got it.

00:07:29.208 --> 00:07:30.375
[PUPPET 1]
Cursed.

00:07:30.417 --> 00:07:31.958
-[PUPPET 2] Cursed.
-[PUPPET 3] Cursed.

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:34.292
-[PUPPET 4] Cursed!
-[PUPPET 5] Cursed!

00:07:34.333 --> 00:07:37.167
[PUPPETS in unison]
Cursed!

00:07:37.208 --> 00:07:39.125
Alright, practice begins now.

00:07:39.167 --> 00:07:40.167
Okay!

00:07:40.208 --> 00:07:42.667
[CLARA]
Yay! Bring it!

00:07:42.708 --> 00:07:43.958
[IRUMA]
Whoa!

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:45.333
[PUPPETS]
Cursed. Cursed. Cursed.

00:07:45.375 --> 00:07:47.625
-[CLARA chuckles]
-[PUPPET 1] Cursed!

00:07:47.667 --> 00:07:49.000
[PUPPET 2]
Cursed!

00:07:49.042 --> 00:07:50.333
[PUPPET 3]
Cursed. Cursed.

00:07:50.375 --> 00:07:51.458
-[ASMODEUS] Here I go.
-[PUPPET 4] Cursed.

00:07:51.500 --> 00:07:52.500
-[CLARA] Come on.
-[PUPPET 5] Cursed.

00:07:52.542 --> 00:07:54.792
-[IRUMA] Yay!
-[PUPPET 1] Cursed.

00:07:54.833 --> 00:07:56.792
-[laughs]
-[PUPPETS] Cursed. Cursed.

00:07:56.833 --> 00:07:58.667
This is just dodgeball!

00:08:01.292 --> 00:08:04.000
I sort of pieced it together
during the rundown, but...

00:08:04.042 --> 00:08:05.833
-[PUPPET] Cursed?
-What, is something wrong?

00:08:05.875 --> 00:08:07.750
I can't drop my guard!

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:11.583
Then again, the netherworld
can be pretty laid-back.

00:08:11.625 --> 00:08:13.375
If we're just
playing dodgeball, even I...

00:08:13.417 --> 00:08:15.125
[whimpers]

00:08:22.542 --> 00:08:25.125
[groans in fear]

00:08:25.167 --> 00:08:27.000
[gasps] Sabnock? What?

00:08:27.042 --> 00:08:29.833
[SABNOCK] A death battle
to climb the ranks.

00:08:29.875 --> 00:08:31.958
Thou did not disappoint.

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:33.458
[JAZZ]
Oh, there you are.

00:08:33.500 --> 00:08:35.500
We're bored, so how 'bout
letting us play, too?

00:08:35.542 --> 00:08:37.458
[BOTH]
Let's play. Let us play.

00:08:37.500 --> 00:08:39.583
[SCHNEIDER] Harmony is
the greatest of virtues.

00:08:39.625 --> 00:08:42.375
This is such an annoying pain.

00:08:42.417 --> 00:08:43.792
[IRUMA]
Guys!

00:08:43.833 --> 00:08:47.042
Ha, ha! Get ready
for maximum merriment!

00:08:47.083 --> 00:08:48.542
[GOEMON]
Huh.

00:08:48.583 --> 00:08:50.583
Special technique...

00:08:53.958 --> 00:08:55.292
Wind-Sword Kill.

00:08:55.333 --> 00:08:58.917
♪

00:08:58.958 --> 00:08:59.917
[whimpers]

00:08:59.958 --> 00:09:00.917
[yawns]

00:09:00.958 --> 00:09:02.417
[shrieks]

00:09:02.458 --> 00:09:03.917
[groans]

00:09:06.042 --> 00:09:07.417
[grunts]

00:09:09.167 --> 00:09:10.667
So loud.

00:09:10.708 --> 00:09:12.417
I'm not done yet.

00:09:12.458 --> 00:09:14.667
Take this and this and this!

00:09:17.208 --> 00:09:19.875
Check it out,
that guy is a beast.

00:09:19.917 --> 00:09:21.917
-You boys want candies?
-Huh?

00:09:21.958 --> 00:09:23.583
[IRUMA]
This isn't laid-back at all.

00:09:24.625 --> 00:09:27.083
I'll be waiting, alright?

00:09:27.125 --> 00:09:29.208
[IRUMA]
Ameri, I'm sorry.

00:09:29.250 --> 00:09:32.083
I can't climb the ranks,
not like this.

00:09:32.125 --> 00:09:35.458
No. Training won't exactly
help me out here.

00:09:35.500 --> 00:09:37.208
Did you say "training,"
Iruma sir?

00:09:37.250 --> 00:09:39.333
-Huh?
-You must want to train.

00:09:39.375 --> 00:09:40.958
Um, actually...

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:43.167
There is the possibility
that you'll attain

00:09:43.208 --> 00:09:45.917
an immeasurable rank again,
Master Iruma.

00:09:45.958 --> 00:09:48.333
We need to be extra careful.

00:09:48.375 --> 00:09:50.125
But I'm concerned I won't be

00:09:50.167 --> 00:09:53.292
a substantial enough opponent
for your training.

00:09:53.333 --> 00:09:55.042
Why don't you discuss
this matter with someone

00:09:55.083 --> 00:09:58.333
who's already in possession
of a much higher rank?

00:09:58.375 --> 00:10:00.458
[IRUMA]
Yeah, but who do you mean?

00:10:00.500 --> 00:10:01.750
[ASMODEUS]
Well, it's someone

00:10:01.792 --> 00:10:04.042
you're quite familiar with,
Master Iruma.

00:10:04.083 --> 00:10:05.750
Is it really?

00:10:05.792 --> 00:10:08.500
♪

00:10:12.500 --> 00:10:14.458
[SULLIVAN]
I see now.

00:10:16.500 --> 00:10:19.500
If you please,
and don't mince words,

00:10:19.542 --> 00:10:21.708
tell me more
about this training.

00:10:23.042 --> 00:10:24.542
[thunder cracks]

00:10:24.583 --> 00:10:26.250
♪

00:10:33.250 --> 00:10:35.792
Where the hell
did those little heathens go?

00:10:36.875 --> 00:10:38.583
[thunder cracks]

00:10:40.000 --> 00:10:44.000
♪

00:10:48.833 --> 00:10:50.250
[evil laughter]

00:10:50.292 --> 00:10:51.458
[NARRATOR]
Friend or foe,

00:10:51.500 --> 00:10:54.167
Iruma's completely
surrounded by demons.

00:10:54.208 --> 00:10:56.500
The difference in strength
between Iruma and the others

00:10:56.542 --> 00:10:58.083
is beyond evident.

00:10:59.250 --> 00:11:01.250
[IRUMA] There's nothing else
I can possibly do

00:11:01.292 --> 00:11:03.667
about this right now, so...

00:11:05.083 --> 00:11:08.542
I just wanted to thank you
for training me, chair demon.

00:11:09.583 --> 00:11:11.792
How many times must I tell you?

00:11:11.833 --> 00:11:15.042
You're supposed to call me
Grandpa outside of school.

00:11:15.083 --> 00:11:16.500
Why do you think
we bothered coming

00:11:16.542 --> 00:11:18.375
all the way back home
to do this, my boy?

00:11:18.417 --> 00:11:21.125
Oh. I... My mistake.

00:11:21.167 --> 00:11:24.000
I thought
we came home to train.

00:11:24.042 --> 00:11:28.042
Okay, let's give it
a light throw, how about that?

00:11:28.083 --> 00:11:29.750
Aim for that rock.

00:11:31.333 --> 00:11:33.500
Uh, that looks pretty far.

00:11:33.542 --> 00:11:35.292
I'm really bad at these things.

00:11:35.333 --> 00:11:38.417
Oh, you'll be fine
as long as you do just as I say.

00:11:38.458 --> 00:11:40.708
Stand just a little bit wider.

00:11:40.750 --> 00:11:42.875
Uh, is this right?

00:11:42.917 --> 00:11:44.250
Yes, perfect.

00:11:44.292 --> 00:11:46.833
Also, don't stiffen
your right arm too much.

00:11:46.875 --> 00:11:48.542
[IRUMA]
Oh. Okay.

00:11:48.583 --> 00:11:50.500
[SULLIVAN]
Now, give it a hurl.

00:11:50.542 --> 00:11:54.333
[IRUMA] I was imagining some
crazy, unorthodox technique,

00:11:54.375 --> 00:11:56.917
but this is basically
just regular dodgeball.

00:11:57.958 --> 00:12:00.500
Huh. Okay, I'll give it a shot.

00:12:00.542 --> 00:12:04.083
Oh, and when you throw, yell,
"Li-be-ra."

00:12:04.125 --> 00:12:05.083
[IRUMA]
Wait, what?

00:12:05.125 --> 00:12:07.583
And, Li-be-ra!

00:12:09.667 --> 00:12:10.625
[grunts]

00:12:12.917 --> 00:12:14.375
[roars]

00:12:17.167 --> 00:12:18.375
-[SULLIVAN] Whoo!
-[IRUMA gasps]

00:12:21.208 --> 00:12:22.875
[SULLIVAN]
Well done.

00:12:22.917 --> 00:12:25.292
You'll annihilate them,
no doubt.

00:12:25.333 --> 00:12:26.333
Training is over.

00:12:26.375 --> 00:12:27.958
This is a terrible mistake.

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:29.333
I can't use magic!

00:12:29.375 --> 00:12:32.250
Aw, but why not? It's so easy.

00:12:32.292 --> 00:12:33.708
-[IRUMA] Um...
-[SULLIVAN] Hmm?

00:12:33.750 --> 00:12:35.500
Well, what I mean is,

00:12:35.542 --> 00:12:37.708
I would be using your power.

00:12:37.750 --> 00:12:39.167
I can't cheat.

00:12:40.583 --> 00:12:44.375
It's important that I find a way
to do this on my own.

00:12:44.417 --> 00:12:45.792
So no magic.

00:12:45.833 --> 00:12:47.083
[SULLIVAN sighs]

00:12:48.583 --> 00:12:50.083
[chuckles]

00:12:50.125 --> 00:12:54.083
Admirable, but that will put you
at a distinct disadvantage.

00:12:55.167 --> 00:12:56.458
Therefore, child...

00:12:58.167 --> 00:12:59.375
[IRUMA gasps]

00:12:59.417 --> 00:13:02.542
I just strengthened
your hands a little bit.

00:13:02.583 --> 00:13:05.292
That way, you can
at least catch any ball

00:13:05.333 --> 00:13:06.875
a demon might throw at you.

00:13:06.917 --> 00:13:10.333
I'm a firm believer in
a level playing field, you see.

00:13:11.667 --> 00:13:13.542
Thank you, Grandpa.

00:13:13.583 --> 00:13:15.167
[camera shutter clicks]

00:13:15.208 --> 00:13:17.292
[SULLIVAN]
Wholesome.

00:13:17.333 --> 00:13:20.125
[shuddering]

00:13:20.167 --> 00:13:22.708
Are... you okay?

00:13:22.750 --> 00:13:24.875
[SULLIVAN] I'm saving that image
to my heart's memory.

00:13:24.917 --> 00:13:27.125
I need to make sure
I put a file lock on it.

00:13:27.167 --> 00:13:29.125
Memo. A lock? Hang on.

00:13:29.167 --> 00:13:31.208
Thank you, Grandpa.
Thank you, Grandpa.

00:13:31.250 --> 00:13:34.167
Thank you, Grandpa.
Thank you, Grandpa.

00:13:34.208 --> 00:13:36.375
Devi, devi, devi.

00:13:36.417 --> 00:13:38.625
-Okay, I'll be going now.
-Huh?

00:13:38.667 --> 00:13:40.167
And don't you worry
about anything.

00:13:40.208 --> 00:13:42.958
If you really want to train
without using magic,

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:45.167
I know of a much
better teacher for you.

00:13:45.208 --> 00:13:47.917
Hmm? [gasps]

00:13:50.833 --> 00:13:54.542
From here on out I shall be
taking over your mentorship.

00:13:54.583 --> 00:13:55.958
[IRUMA]
Opera?

00:13:56.958 --> 00:13:59.667
Okay. I'll leave
the rest up to you.

00:14:01.250 --> 00:14:03.167
Make me proud, now.

00:14:03.208 --> 00:14:05.042
[IRUMA'S VOICE]
Thank you, Grandpa.

00:14:05.083 --> 00:14:06.292
[IRUMA grunts]

00:14:07.375 --> 00:14:09.167
Okay, let's begin.

00:14:09.208 --> 00:14:10.417
[IRUMA]
Wait!

00:14:11.708 --> 00:14:12.917
Hang on!

00:14:12.958 --> 00:14:14.708
Give me a second!

00:14:14.750 --> 00:14:16.792
Time stops for no one.

00:14:16.833 --> 00:14:18.458
[BAT grunts]

00:14:18.500 --> 00:14:19.583
Hold up!

00:14:19.625 --> 00:14:20.708
Wait!

00:14:20.750 --> 00:14:22.083
I'm begging you!

00:14:22.125 --> 00:14:23.250
Opera!

00:14:23.292 --> 00:14:25.583
[gasps] Why?!

00:14:25.625 --> 00:14:27.833
[panting]

00:14:27.875 --> 00:14:29.250
[OPERA]
As I thought,

00:14:29.292 --> 00:14:32.458
you are a true master
of evasion, young Iruma.

00:14:32.500 --> 00:14:34.250
But if you want
to move up the ranks,

00:14:34.292 --> 00:14:35.667
you have to do more than that,

00:14:35.708 --> 00:14:38.333
you must actually be able
to hit your foe.

00:14:38.375 --> 00:14:39.917
[IRUMA]
Oh.

00:14:39.958 --> 00:14:42.333
[panting]
Is that all?

00:14:42.375 --> 00:14:43.333
Correct.

00:14:43.375 --> 00:14:45.208
[grunts]

00:14:47.042 --> 00:14:49.167
First, let's try
catching a ball.

00:14:49.208 --> 00:14:52.833
As much as this pains me,
I'm going to keep throwing them.

00:14:52.875 --> 00:14:55.875
[screams] Wait! This is crazy!

00:14:55.917 --> 00:14:57.875
Oh, this pains me so.

00:14:57.917 --> 00:15:01.125
There's no expression
on your face whatsoever!

00:15:01.167 --> 00:15:04.875
[OPERA] I'm doing this so you
don't get hurt in a real match.

00:15:04.917 --> 00:15:08.250
And if you truly wish
to ascend to a higher rank,

00:15:08.292 --> 00:15:11.250
it will mean even more
stringent guidance drills.

00:15:11.292 --> 00:15:13.875
-[IRUMA groaning]
-Prepare yourself accordingly.

00:15:13.917 --> 00:15:16.917
[IRUMA screams]

00:15:16.958 --> 00:15:19.167
[BATS screech]

00:15:19.208 --> 00:15:20.833
That'll be all for today.

00:15:20.875 --> 00:15:22.000
Okay.

00:15:23.667 --> 00:15:24.875
Catch this.

00:15:25.875 --> 00:15:27.292
But how?

00:15:27.333 --> 00:15:29.125
[chimes]

00:15:29.167 --> 00:15:32.375
[ASMODEUS] Iruma sir,
how goes your training?

00:15:32.417 --> 00:15:34.667
Please allow me
to offer my support.

00:15:34.708 --> 00:15:35.750
We're friends, after all.

00:15:35.792 --> 00:15:37.083
No need to reply.

00:15:37.125 --> 00:15:39.167
I'm just honored
you read my messages.

00:15:39.208 --> 00:15:41.667
[CLARA] Go, go, Iruma-kins.
Devi, devi, go, go.

00:15:41.708 --> 00:15:43.208
[ASMODEUS]
Even here you interrupt me?

00:15:43.250 --> 00:15:46.167
-[CLARA] Devi, devi, go, go.
-[IRUMA] Azz and Clara, too.

00:15:46.208 --> 00:15:48.208
[ASMODEUS]
I said, listen.

00:15:48.250 --> 00:15:49.333
[IRUMA]
Thank you.

00:15:51.208 --> 00:15:54.250
Oh, yeah, I should probably
report back to Ameri, too.

00:15:56.542 --> 00:15:57.917
Iruma sir.

00:15:57.958 --> 00:16:00.375
Fight, fight, fight!

00:16:00.417 --> 00:16:03.667
Today we shall continue
our catching lessons.

00:16:03.708 --> 00:16:04.750
[IRUMA]
Right.

00:16:06.625 --> 00:16:08.333
[grunts nervously]

00:16:08.375 --> 00:16:11.167
[OPERA] Whenever the ball
is about to hit your face,

00:16:11.208 --> 00:16:12.667
I will stop it like so.

00:16:12.708 --> 00:16:14.917
Rather than dodging it,
try to catch it.

00:16:14.958 --> 00:16:16.708
Okay.

00:16:16.750 --> 00:16:18.958
[screaming]

00:16:19.000 --> 00:16:23.333
Sorry. I don't mean to,
my body has a mind of its own.

00:16:23.375 --> 00:16:24.708
[OPERA]
Please listen.

00:16:24.750 --> 00:16:26.458
You have to keep
your eye on the ball

00:16:26.500 --> 00:16:29.042
and truly concentrate.

00:16:29.083 --> 00:16:31.125
Now let's try it again,
Iruma sir.

00:16:31.167 --> 00:16:32.500
Okay.

00:16:32.542 --> 00:16:34.417
One, two, catch!

00:16:36.000 --> 00:16:39.458
[IRUMA] Just keep
my eyes on the... ball.

00:16:40.583 --> 00:16:41.500
[screams]

00:16:41.542 --> 00:16:43.250
Now grab it, quickly.

00:16:43.292 --> 00:16:44.500
[yells]

00:16:44.542 --> 00:16:46.500
I can't.

00:16:46.542 --> 00:16:47.500
Iruma sir!

00:16:47.542 --> 00:16:49.500
Come on.

00:16:49.542 --> 00:16:51.125
[grunts] Hmph!

00:16:53.167 --> 00:16:54.875
[yells]

00:16:54.917 --> 00:16:56.875
[BOTH gasp]

00:16:56.917 --> 00:16:58.875
[OPERA]
That's the spirit.

00:16:58.917 --> 00:17:01.833
Ground your lower body
and focus harder.

00:17:04.625 --> 00:17:05.708
Got it.

00:17:10.208 --> 00:17:12.083
[AMERI]
Iruma has begun his training.

00:17:13.750 --> 00:17:14.917
So we'll have to put the reading

00:17:14.958 --> 00:17:17.458
of the forbidden texts on hold.

00:17:17.500 --> 00:17:18.500
It's inevitable.

00:17:19.500 --> 00:17:22.458
I shall wait until
his exam is complete.

00:17:24.208 --> 00:17:25.375
Good luck, Iruma.

00:17:26.583 --> 00:17:28.125
-Do your best.
-[grunting]

00:17:28.167 --> 00:17:30.375
Yes, strengthen those muscles.

00:17:30.417 --> 00:17:31.458
You can do it.

00:17:31.500 --> 00:17:32.708
Come on, fight.

00:17:32.750 --> 00:17:34.708
[grunting]

00:17:36.750 --> 00:17:39.250
-[groans]
-You got this, Iruma-kins!

00:17:39.292 --> 00:17:40.208
Lift me up, higher.

00:17:40.250 --> 00:17:41.958
Will you stop interfering?

00:17:43.292 --> 00:17:45.500
[panting]

00:17:45.542 --> 00:17:46.708
[OPERA]
Faster, move it.

00:17:50.167 --> 00:17:51.375
[IRUMA]
Catch.

00:17:51.417 --> 00:17:53.792
[panting continues]

00:17:57.917 --> 00:17:58.875
Catch.

00:18:03.042 --> 00:18:05.500
[panting continues]

00:18:07.208 --> 00:18:08.417
Catch.

00:18:08.458 --> 00:18:11.375
♪

00:18:14.708 --> 00:18:16.250
-[ASMODEUS] Iruma sir.
-Huh?

00:18:16.292 --> 00:18:17.708
Some water.

00:18:17.750 --> 00:18:19.958
Azz, thanks a lot.

00:18:20.000 --> 00:18:22.000
Here's more food, keep eating.

00:18:22.042 --> 00:18:24.000
I see your appetite
is still healthy.

00:18:24.042 --> 00:18:24.917
I guess so.

00:18:26.375 --> 00:18:27.417
-[IRUMA gasps]
-[gasps sharply]

00:18:27.458 --> 00:18:30.000
Iruma sir! Your hand.

00:18:30.833 --> 00:18:33.542
Oh, it's wounded
so grievously!

00:18:33.583 --> 00:18:35.792
Yeah. The ball will
actually hit my hands

00:18:35.833 --> 00:18:37.167
about half the time now.

00:18:37.208 --> 00:18:38.167
[ASMODEUS]
Hmm.

00:18:38.208 --> 00:18:39.750
Also, I think I'm finally

00:18:39.792 --> 00:18:40.833
starting to recognize

00:18:40.875 --> 00:18:42.417
all of Opera's
different moods.

00:18:42.458 --> 00:18:45.250
When their kitty ears droop,
they're in a bad mood.

00:18:45.292 --> 00:18:47.500
When the ears are pointed up,
they're in a good mood.

00:18:47.542 --> 00:18:49.500
-Wow.
-Interesting.

00:18:51.000 --> 00:18:53.167
[humming]

00:18:53.208 --> 00:18:55.750
Catch it. Catch it.

00:18:57.042 --> 00:18:58.500
He's amazing, isn't he?

00:18:58.542 --> 00:19:00.083
Demons usually bore easily.

00:19:01.167 --> 00:19:02.917
-[ASMODEUS] Indeed.
-Huh?

00:19:02.958 --> 00:19:05.542
Master Iruma is...

00:19:05.583 --> 00:19:07.375
uniquely eccentric.

00:19:08.375 --> 00:19:10.667
Okay, back to training I go!

00:19:10.708 --> 00:19:12.583
[ASMODEUS AND CLARA]
Yeah!

00:19:12.625 --> 00:19:13.792
[CLARA]
Take that!

00:19:13.833 --> 00:19:17.292
♪

00:19:22.500 --> 00:19:26.292
[breathing heavily]

00:19:31.583 --> 00:19:34.667
[SULLIVAN] He's clearly
worked hard again today.

00:19:34.708 --> 00:19:36.500
So, how is the training going?

00:19:36.542 --> 00:19:38.625
Do you think
he'll make it in time?

00:19:38.667 --> 00:19:41.042
[OPERA] He still has yet
to catch the ball even once.

00:19:41.083 --> 00:19:43.167
Oh, no! Is he going to succeed?

00:19:43.208 --> 00:19:44.542
Will he be able to do it?

00:19:44.583 --> 00:19:46.500
[OPERA]
However...

00:19:46.542 --> 00:19:47.583
[SULLIVAN]
Hmm?

00:19:47.625 --> 00:19:48.958
[OPERA]
He seems to be having

00:19:49.000 --> 00:19:50.958
more and more fun every day.

00:19:52.917 --> 00:19:54.625
Well, that's wonderful.

00:19:57.458 --> 00:19:59.875
-[IRUMA panting]
-[heart thumps]

00:20:02.917 --> 00:20:04.583
[OPERA]
The promotion exam is tomorrow.

00:20:04.625 --> 00:20:06.583
Time to give it your all.

00:20:06.625 --> 00:20:07.750
[grunts]

00:20:07.792 --> 00:20:09.208
[IRUMA]
Just a little more.

00:20:10.583 --> 00:20:12.375
[grunts]

00:20:12.417 --> 00:20:14.375
-Iruma sir!
-Iruma-kins!

00:20:14.417 --> 00:20:16.042
[heart thumps]

00:20:16.083 --> 00:20:17.250
[grunts]

00:20:17.292 --> 00:20:18.958
[IRUMA]
This is it.

00:20:19.000 --> 00:20:20.250
Another one!

00:20:20.292 --> 00:20:21.583
Here they come.

00:20:21.625 --> 00:20:22.750
[grunts]

00:20:25.458 --> 00:20:28.250
[IRUMA] Get down,
ground my lower body,

00:20:28.292 --> 00:20:29.500
and then...

00:20:30.625 --> 00:20:32.167
[grunts]

00:20:32.208 --> 00:20:34.167
Keep your eyes on the ball.

00:20:34.208 --> 00:20:35.667
[grunts]

00:20:37.292 --> 00:20:38.917
[IRUMA]
Keep my eyes...

00:20:40.250 --> 00:20:41.917
on the ball!

00:20:41.958 --> 00:20:43.667
[BOTH gasp]

00:20:43.708 --> 00:20:45.000
[heart thumps]

00:20:46.083 --> 00:20:47.333
Make sure...

00:20:50.708 --> 00:20:51.917
[chuckles softly]

00:20:51.958 --> 00:20:53.917
...to watch the ball!

00:20:53.958 --> 00:20:56.500
♪

00:20:56.542 --> 00:20:57.792
[grunts]

00:20:59.708 --> 00:21:02.417
[BOTH]
Oh! Wow!

00:21:02.458 --> 00:21:04.250
[BOTH gasp]

00:21:06.042 --> 00:21:07.417
Yes, I caught it!

00:21:07.458 --> 00:21:08.625
That was splendid.

00:21:08.667 --> 00:21:10.542
High five, high five, devi five!

00:21:10.583 --> 00:21:11.583
[CLARA AND IRUMA]
Yay!

00:21:11.625 --> 00:21:12.875
[ASMODEUS]
Hey, wait a minute.

00:21:12.917 --> 00:21:15.375
Master Iruma's hands
are still gravely injured.

00:21:15.417 --> 00:21:16.625
I'm fine.

00:21:16.667 --> 00:21:18.208
Did you wanna try, too?

00:21:18.250 --> 00:21:19.958
[ASMODEUS]
Oh, uh, may I?

00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:24.000
[IRUMA chuckles]

00:21:24.042 --> 00:21:27.458
Devi five. Devi five.
Devi five, five.

00:21:27.500 --> 00:21:28.833
-Devi, devi, five, five.
-[OPERA] Let us continue

00:21:28.875 --> 00:21:30.583
before this feeling wears off.

00:21:30.625 --> 00:21:32.667
[IRUMA gasps]

00:21:33.625 --> 00:21:35.208
After we've finished
our training,

00:21:35.250 --> 00:21:37.500
I shall prepare a most
sumptuous dinner for you.

00:21:38.500 --> 00:21:39.958
[gasps]

00:21:40.000 --> 00:21:41.000
Okay.

00:21:41.042 --> 00:21:44.708
♪

00:21:46.083 --> 00:21:47.042
[SULLIVAN]
Looks like he's as ready

00:21:47.083 --> 00:21:49.667
as he could possibly be.

00:21:49.708 --> 00:21:51.083
[OPERA]
Yes.

00:21:51.125 --> 00:21:54.375
♪

00:21:54.417 --> 00:21:57.167
[CLARA AND IRUMA
breathing heavily]

00:21:59.750 --> 00:22:00.875
Quite ready.

00:22:03.417 --> 00:22:05.417
♪

00:23:37.875 --> 00:23:41.208
Su-ki-ma. Su-ki-ma. Su-ki-ma!

00:23:41.250 --> 00:23:43.875
Ameri, I'm so sorry
I haven't been able to read

00:23:43.917 --> 00:23:46.208
"First Love Memories"
to you lately.

00:23:46.250 --> 00:23:48.958
[AMERI] It's true I can't wait
to hear what happens next,

00:23:49.000 --> 00:23:51.333
but I'd also like him
to take his training seriously

00:23:51.375 --> 00:23:53.417
so he can ascend the ranks.

00:23:53.458 --> 00:23:55.958
That's right. There was
a scene in the forbidden texts

00:23:56.000 --> 00:23:58.500
where they spoke honestly
about their feelings.

00:23:58.542 --> 00:24:01.750
I'll use that same method to
tell him how I'm truly feeling.

00:24:02.500 --> 00:24:04.208
Iruma!

00:24:04.250 --> 00:24:05.375
[IRUMA screams]

00:24:07.375 --> 00:24:09.250
About our reading sessions...

00:24:09.292 --> 00:24:11.875
So you are mad about it,
I was right.

00:24:11.917 --> 00:24:13.500
[NARRATOR]
The wall slam has failed.

00:24:13.542 --> 00:24:16.500
♪

00:24:16.542 --> 00:24:18.042
[SULLIVAN]
You're working so hard, Iruma.

00:24:18.083 --> 00:24:19.458
Grandpa's so happy.

00:24:19.500 --> 00:24:21.333
By the way, I've been recording
all of your hard work,

00:24:21.375 --> 00:24:23.292
so we'll have it forever.

00:24:23.333 --> 00:24:26.250
I have all the latest tech,
and even 666K.

00:24:26.292 --> 00:24:28.000
Maybe I'll surprise you
with this footage

00:24:28.042 --> 00:24:29.375
when you get married someday.

00:24:29.417 --> 00:24:30.417
Ooh!

00:24:31.333 --> 00:24:35.667
Next time, "Fierce Battle,
Execution Cannonball."

00:24:35.708 --> 00:24:37.125
Iruma, he's our guy.

00:24:37.167 --> 00:24:38.917
Make those
devi dodgeballs fly.

00:24:38.958 --> 00:24:41.000
♪

